Articles.Content: Is there any link to get Klockheed Martian's stuff that includes the skylab, because I'd really like to make a story about the progression of KSP.
Are you confusing this with Raidernicks Skylab?

I think he is talking about this mod:

It was by dtobi, but raidernick took it over.  The end of that thread looks like some drama, then the thread was locked. 

 

Sad, because there were some cool parts in there. They just don't work anymore.

The Klockheed Martian thread was locked by request of Raidernick but last edited the Original Post on December 3rd so maybe he is working on upgrading it to 1.0.5 and just wanted the thread locked till then.
